summary: This texture mod changes the appearance of crates
descriptionHtml:
Washed Skyrim

How about some cool boxes? Wonderful! They fit and bags, and baskets!

Ver 0.2
Author: Ri4

Description
This texture mod changes the appearance of crates

______________________________

Installation
Use NMM or Move the files to your data directory

Uninstall
Use NMM or Delete the files from your date directory
